# Data Dictionary — arts2021_patent_nlp

## Data source
All USPTO utility patents granted up to May 2018 — Full-text US patent claims/descriptions for NLP novelty+impact+breakthrough indicators
Access: public; Provenance: Zenodo 10.5281/zenodo.3515985 (static bulk)

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: patent
- Time window: USPTO coverage to 2018-05
- Sample N: all USPTO utility patents to 2018-05
- Filter rules: utility patents, award-linked case-control subset

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: NLP-based novelty/impact/breakthrough measures on patent text; validated vs classification+citation baselines
- Parameters: n-gram/term extraction, award case-control validation
- Computation steps: extract patent text, compute NLP novelty/impact, validate vs awards
